---
id: my_agent_21
name: Basic Agent
description: A basic prompt that uses the gpt-4o chat API to answer questions
metadata:
  authors:
    - sethjuarez
    - jietong
  tags:
    - basic
    - gpt-4o
model:
  api: chat
  connection:
    type: azure_openai
    azure_deployment: gpt-4o
  options:
    max_tokens: 150
    temperature: 0.5
    top_p: 1
    frequency_penalty: 0
    presence_penalty: 0
inputs:
  firstName:
    type: string
    default: User
    sample: April
    description: The first name of the customer
  lastName:
    type: string
    sample: Kwong
    required: true
    strict: false
    description: The last name of the customer
  question:
    type: string
    description: The question to answer
    required: true
outputs:
  work:
    type: object
    json_schema: ${file:schema.json}
    description: The thing to output

tools:
  - name: coder
    type: openai.CodeInterpreter
    configuration:
      connection: "https://contoso.crm.dynamics.com"
      other: "other"
  
template:
  format: mustache
  parser: prompty
---
tools:
  - name: query
    type: dataverse
    configuration:
      connection: "https://contoso.crm.dynamics.com"
      query: SELECT * FROM Customers WHERE firstName = '{{firstName}}' AND lastName = '{{lastName}}'
  - name: search
    type: bing
    configuration:
      parameters: [{{question}}]

system:
You are an AI assistant who helps people find information.
As the assistant, you answer questions briefly, succinctly, 
and in a personable manner using markdown and even add some personal flair with appropriate emojis.

# Customer
You are helping {{firstName}} {{lastName}} to find answers to their questions.
Use their name to address them in your responses.

assistant[type="tool_call"]:
id: tool_call_123
type: function
function:
  name: get_account_info
  arguments:
    account_number: 123456

assistant:
other thing in here too

user[name="{{firstName}} {{lastName}}"]:
bn bn bnb {{question}}  hnghnhg
{{ desds  sd}}